high_descs: Turn to your right, then walk across the kitchen to the coffee machine.
Pick up a black mug from the coffee machine.
Turn to your left and walk towards the microwave.
Place the cup in the microwave and warm it.
Turn to around and go back to the coffee machine.
Place the cup back in the coffee machine.
anns.task_desc: Place a warmed cup in a coffee machine.

high_descs: Turn around towards the door and then turn left towards the stove and then turn right towards the coffee maker.
Pick up the grey cup from the coffee maker.
Open the microwave, place the cup inside, close the microwave to heat it, and open the microwave to take the cup out.
Turn around and head towards the coffee maker on your left.
Place the cup on to the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Heat up the cup on the coffee maker.

high_descs: Pick up the mug from the coffee machine.
Bring the mug to the microwave.
Heat the mug in the microwave.
Bring the mug to the coffee machine.
Put the mug in the coffee machine.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated mug in the coffee machine.
